```{r ampulla 31465765, include=FALSE}

PMID_31465765 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('31465765', database = 'PubMed')

citation_31465765 <- paste0(PMID_31465765$journal,' ', PMID_31465765$year, ' ', PMID_31465765$month,';', PMID_31465765$volume,'(', PMID_31465765$number,'):', PMID_31465765$pages)

PubMed_31465765 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_31465765$eprint)

doi_31465765 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_31465765$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
